{"tid":1681660,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"叫deliveroo撞到前度，之後佢...","createTime":"2019-10-29T14:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T12:39:10.000Z","uid":209657,"like":7,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"96da396d92cd74ec24069d7c0698005f3a5adc0a","tid":1681660,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:34:53.000Z","msg":"我頭先喺屋企肚餓<br />\n男朋友出左trip 得返我自己一個 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夜晚晚我一個女仔落街好危險架嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有用deliveroo嗌宵夜食啦<br />\norder完之後發現 車手個名竟然同我ex一樣！<br />\n嚇到我心都離一離！！不過諗住唔會咁啱嘅！<br />\n<br />\n叮咚～～外賣到！<br />\n一開門發現原來真係我前度！！<br />\n佢用把好性感既聲同我講 好耐無見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見佢身水身汗 件背心仔濕晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就即刻入房攞條毛巾俾佢抹<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知...佢...竟然跟左我入房....<br />\n之後我地.....<br />\n<br />\n佢個電話一直響 應該係有人催單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就dum左佢個電話落地<br />\n點知唔小心整爆左個mon<br />\n所以我想問各位巴打<br />\n知唔知邊度可以整mon？<br />\nThanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5071a75cb5dc9ee7bf5588eebe3917f68abaeaaf","tid":1681660,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:35:52.000Z","msg":"地政處就元朗中資銀行 僭建圍板非法佔用土地發出清拆令<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681312</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6947d0eb0e05ee49c043377df65a39e07910ed0b","tid":1681660,"uid":323175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"咁似台灣嗰單咩熊貓外送既"},{"pid":"634ae9d88f0b5f790e57d66724737e7aa7ef3fac","tid":1681660,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:59:31.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"d4ed27e604a67005394626d8370cfdb7a09f8088","tid":16